# containers/vllm/config/config.env.example
#
# Mounted-config-file alternative to `docker run -e ...`. Copy this to e.g.
# /opt/vllm/config.env on the host, edit as needed, and mount it into the
# container at /etc/vllm/config.env (see docker-compose.yml / README.md).
#
# Precedence: if this file is mounted, every value it sets wins over the
# same-named `docker run -e` env var, which in turn wins over the built-in
# default in entrypoint.sh. Leave a line commented out to fall through to
# whatever `docker run -e` (or the built-in default) provides.
#
# This file is sourced by entrypoint.sh with `set -a`, so plain KEY=value
# assignments are enough — no `export` needed.

# --- Model / precision -------------------------------------------------
# Default: Qwen's own published FP8 checkpoint (fine-grained block-128 FP8,
# ~29 GiB on disk/VRAM) — verified to exist at huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3.6-27B-FP8.
# MODEL_ID=Qwen/Qwen3.6-27B-FP8

# INT4/AWQ path: Qwen does not publish an official INT4/AWQ checkpoint for
# Qwen3.6-27B as of this writing. Community checkpoints exist (verify
# provenance before using in anything beyond this lab) - e.g.:
# MODEL_ID=QuantTrio/Qwen3.6-27B-AWQ
# QUANTIZATION=awq

# SERVED_MODEL_NAME=Qwen/Qwen3.6-27B-FP8

# --- Memory / KV-cache sizing (see README.md "Sizing rationale") -------
# GPU_MEMORY_UTILIZATION=0.90
# MAX_MODEL_LEN=32768
# MAX_NUM_SEQS=64
# KV_CACHE_DTYPE=auto

# --- KV-cache management strategy knobs ---------------------------------
# ENABLE_PREFIX_CACHING=true
# ENABLE_CHUNKED_PREFILL=true

# --- Tool calling / reasoning (load-bearing for agent-builder) ---------
# ENABLE_TOOL_CALLING=true
# TOOL_CALL_PARSER=qwen3_coder
# REASONING_PARSER=qwen3

# --- Multimodal ----------------------------------------------------------
# Qwen3.6-27B ships a vision tower; this lab only drives text/agentic
# traffic, so the default skips it to free memory for KV cache.
# LANGUAGE_MODEL_ONLY=true

# --- Network -------------------------------------------------------------
# HOST=0.0.0.0
# PORT=8000

# --- Hugging Face auth (optional -- Qwen3.6-27B is NOT gated) -----------
# HF_TOKEN=

# --- Model weight cache (mount to persistent storage) -------------------
# MODEL_CACHE_DIR=/root/.cache/huggingface

# --- Escape hatch: anything else, appended verbatim via eval ------------
# Example: MTP speculative decoding
# EXTRA_VLLM_ARGS=--speculative-config '{"method":"mtp","num_speculative_tokens":2}'
